{"tid":27092,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一次miss左飛機既經驗","createTime":"2016-12-07T06:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T10:49:59.000Z","uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a3a6d53596318f6741f6079e24ef192986b3d7c","tid":27092,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6528edc153eacef5798da6aa4fc40563fad4e2","tid":27092,"uid":26635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:30:08.000Z","msg":"睇錯時間"},{"pid":"431387b9a05b5f7312b5666304259c44502295b3","tid":27092,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:33:42.000Z","msg":"登机闸门前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee868efbea1f571200d8dd3166160f430173fbf8","tid":27092,"uid":35196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"check in左 食野食晏左搞到遲左5分鐘去到閘口<br />\n其實未到起飛時間但架機已經飛左<br />\n仲要比個地勤屌左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知係自己衰唔睇時間<br />\n但係已經miss左班機仲要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b5bd3d4c5116031b025b06ae8c09bad6e00b59","tid":27092,"uid":13391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:35:25.000Z","msg":"預得太忟<br />\n去到櫃臺都閂埋<br />\n喺hostel又漏咗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓上殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d91d8c36a8028a393dfee658a341011ebdb368","tid":27092,"uid":3600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>登机闸门前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢度喺屬於香港人嘅討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27e48cad0aaa1a595cc33d1c7a0b13969daa3f8","tid":27092,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"日上quote 果個block 左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214b8985280c3a42fa1b0d95799b34ae52853fa7","tid":27092,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:43:25.000Z","msg":"同男朋友以及佢朋友，5個人去旅行<br />\n其中一個臨走去買酒想帶上飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n海關定唔知咩工作人員扣起左我地成班審<br />\n枝酒係玻璃樽.....<br />\n再加上佢身上有火柴<br />\n仲有佢想帶煙花番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我第一次係機場比人搜身....比人審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb9485e0e30ef7161b4856984a95c617b481381","tid":27092,"uid":6062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"半年前係paris返香港，因為個terminal封鎖一段時間+豬隊友唔識搵地勤幫手，個時個terminal係好亂，好多人都係趕住check in上機，我地個時連行李都未check in，豬隊友淨係識排緊一條都唔知龍頭係邊嘅隊，淨係靠我一個周圍問又去counter問，又用terminal d電子check in機，最後當然係miss咗班機，要訓機場一晚+罰二千蚊港紙轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906098978061dbd419d24bf2071d3a0d5c2d7e40","tid":27092,"uid":23977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"凌晨5點幾6點機, 自己一個人係外地飛番HK<br />\n3點到左機會check左in入左去候機室附近既coffee shop等<br />\n果晚冇訓過勁眼訓<br />\n之後訓到起飛果一刻先醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁無助搵staff搞佢又唔得閒理我咁<br />\n最後都幫到我改下一班機<br />\n好彩唔洗比多好多錢<br />\n<br />\n之後等下一班機果陣再訓都即刻較番鬧鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2c002aebf1d556e2564bee12e92d3e08c06e60","tid":27092,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:49:59.000Z","msg":"留名待"}]}